{"tid":2392956,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【卡迪夫】空氣水質佳 物價較低","createTime":"2021-02-03T06:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T07:33:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fba9091d05bfb8b100a0e2a637992c01a1680cf8","tid":2392956,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/FEYYQQVI5RBNRPAYKHXKC5RY2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FFEYYQQVI5RBNRPAYKHXKC5RY2U%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=d0cc3d2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FFEYYQQVI5RBNRPAYKHXKC5RY2U%2F&h=340d4567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/FEYYQQVI5RBNRPAYKHXKC5RY2U/</a><br />\n<br />\n【卡迪夫】空氣水質佳 物價較低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/77e719dZ2lay-a8SADog0RsCEt8=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IEXVA4MWKRETPIXZN56PHAQBAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F77e719dZ2lay-a8SADog0RsCEt8%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIEXVA4MWKRETPIXZN56PHAQBAA.jpg&h=bfc0045d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡迪夫<br />\n<br />\n位於西部的威爾斯，是英國四個構成國之一，其首都為卡迪夫（Cardiff），火車距倫敦車程約三小時。曾在卡迪夫讀書兩年的Linus認為，該地人口不多，以其規模計設施算發達，物價亦較英格蘭熱門城市低，近海而不太冷，更可接觸欖球。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【倫敦】侍應、售貨員有力置業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n欖球迷聚腳地<br />\n<br />\n卡迪夫人口近50萬人，整個威爾斯亦只有約315萬人，不及香港一半。Linus認為，若與香港相比，卡迪夫公共交通系統較弱，夜生活少，亦比香港稍冷，但以其人口計，設施算好，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n提及海邊，英國人多聯想到布賴頓（Brighton），是不少倫敦人的度假勝地。Linus指，卡迪夫也是在海旁，且物價較布賴頓稍低。「。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【利鎮】樓價低至70萬有交易<br />\n<br />\n威爾斯是構成國，自設考試委員會，名為WJEC。Linus曾於卡迪夫攻讀高考（GCE A-Level），認為當地教育不錯，更覺得很多科目試卷。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一威爾斯特色是欖球。Linus介紹，欖球在威爾斯是盛事，比賽期間當地酒吧會聚滿欖球迷，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0be7ba7dafae160200195ba40f37109578790bea","tid":2392956,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"卡迪夫城 以家係英超定英甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762fec997de1a8b1172709d1c55e9a0977e82b81","tid":2392956,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"以前卡迪夫千禧球場有得睇杯賽決賽就抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8368d44bcee6c283c594d40a6f302ee0f859eebb","tid":2392956,"uid":240606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"比Xg稍冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91be745a03481562fc221b9664f5d79b29cc6746","tid":2392956,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0be7ba7dafae160200195ba40f37109578790bea","tid":2392956,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"卡迪夫城 以家係英超定英甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"冠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6a8cdc0b730fb95bdbf4d0140331b41399e3fd","tid":2392956,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91be745a03481562fc221b9664f5d79b29cc6746","tid":2392956,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0be7ba7dafae160200195ba40f37109578790bea","tid":2392956,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"卡迪夫城 以家係英超定英甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"冠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-